<HEADLINE>
<P>
GORBACHEV AND CHANGES IN EAST BLOC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Neo-Prussianism should be spotlighted as much as neo-Nazism ("East Germans 
Warned of Neo-Nazism," Part A, Dec. 28). 
</P>
<P>
Already East Germans are demanding return of parts of former Prussia now in 
Poland. 
</P>
<P>
Union with the European Community at Strasbourg is the road to the future. 
Reunion of the Germanys through the Brandenburg Gate is the road back to a 
bloodstained past. 
</P>
<P>
RICHARD CASTELAR SIMONSON 
</P>
<P>
Washington, D.C. 
</P>
</TEXT>
