Mar High School to a 68-53 victory over Woodbridge in a nonleague basketball 
game Friday at Woodbridge. 
</P>
<P>
The Sea Kings (9-6) got off to a slow start and trailed, 16-12, at the end of 
the first quarter. 
</P>
<P>
However, Corona del Mar outscored Woodbridge, 21-12, in the second quarter to 
take a 33-28 halftime lead. 
</P>
<P>
Corona del Mar never trailed in the second half. 
