FANTASY'S FEE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Re the Dec. 13 Morning Report: $96 for a family of four to walk through the 
doors of the Magic Kingdom? "Mercenary Kingdom" is more like it! 
</P>
<P>
CALLY HOOKS, Los Angeles 
