<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010690-0062 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 158264 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 6, 1990, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 5 
