<P>
BANK ROBBERIES -- LOS ANGELES; BOMBS; HOAXES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010690-0103 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 158371 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 6, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
