<HEADLINE>
<P>
AGIRLFROMARS EASY WINNER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Agirlfromars overtook Collective Joy entering the stretch and drew off for a 4 
1/2-length victory in Friday's $47,000 feature race at Santa Anita before a 
crowd of 17,602. 
</P>
<P>
Agirlfromars, the even-money favorite ridden by Robbie Davis and carrying 114 
pounds, covered one mile on Santa Anita's turf course in 1:33 2/5 and paid $4, 
$3 and $2.60. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
