RELEASES; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; VIETNAM -- EMIGRATION; CALIFORNIA -- 
IMMIGRATION; ORANGE COUNTY -- IMMIGRATION; UNITED STATES -- TREATIES -- 
VIETNAM; VIETNAMESE -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
